@startuml
title State Diagram - ScheduledNotificationTask Lifecycle

[*] --> PENDING : task created

PENDING --> PROCESSING : SystemScheduler picks due task
PENDING --> CANCELLED : admin cancels pending task

PROCESSING --> SENT : NotificationService sends notification
PROCESSING --> FAILED : sending fails

FAILED --> PENDING : retry scheduled\nretryCount increased
FAILED --> CANCELLED : admin cancels failed task

SENT --> [*]
CANCELLED --> [*]

note right of PENDING
Task waits until scheduledAt.
end note

note right of PROCESSING
SystemScheduler owns this transition.
end note

note right of FAILED
failureReason stores the problem.
retryCount tracks attempts.
end note

@enduml
